OL,4,Cinfrastructure after inquest into
OL,5,Ccyclist's death
OL,7,FGary McMahon passed away after being
OL,8,Fstruck by a lorry on Clifton Street in
OL,9,FNovember 2024.
OL,11,FThe 58-year-old died of chest and
OL,12,Fabdominal injuries at the scene.
OL,14,FIn delivering her findings at an
OL,15,Finquest into his death, coroner Anne-
OL,16,FLouise Toal said Mr McMahon, who
OL,17,Fworked at the supermarket Asda and the
OL,18,FBBC, had cycled through a red light
OL,19,Fnot realising a lorry was turning.
