OL,7,FShe said the driver of the vehicle
OL,8,Fmade the appropriate number of checks
OL,9,Fduring the turn and the driver had
OL,10,Findicated, but the cyclist was in the
OL,11,F'blind spot'.
OL,13,FThe coroner said it underlines the
OL,14,Fdangers posed to pedestrians and
OL,15,Fcyclists of blindspots associated with
OL,16,Fheavy goods vehicles, 'particularly in
OL,17,Fa country which does not have a
OL,18,Fcomprehensive cycle network'.
