OL,3,CCall for improvements to
OL,4,Cinfrastructure after inquest into
OL,5,Ccyclist's death
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that the vehicle had
OL,8,Fbeen fitted with an additional safety
OL,9,Ffeature to provide alerts about people
OL,10,For objects nearby, but this had not
OL,11,Fbeen working properly at the time of
OL,12,Fthe collision.
OL,14,FIn considering this the coroner stated
OL,15,Fthat additional safety measures can be
OL,16,Ftaken by companies to fit lorries with
OL,17,Fsystems that help drivers detect
OL,18,Fpedestrians or cyclists and which help
OL,19,Fcyclists detect oncoming vehicles.
