OL,7,FSpeaking after the conclusions of the
OL,8,Fverdict, Anne Madden of the Walk,
OL,9,FWheel Cycle Trust said the findings
OL,10,Fshow a need to improve the Clifton
OL,11,FStreet junction.
OL,13,F"The cyclist jumped the red light,
OL,14,Fwhich he shouldn't have done but it
OL,15,Fhighlighted how poor the particular
OL,16,Finfrastructure is in that particular
OL,17,Fpart of Belfast," Anne Madden said.
