OL,4,Cinfrastructure after inquest into
OL,5,Ccyclist's death
OL,7,F"The Clifton Street area has long been
OL,8,Fregarded as unsafe for people cycling
OL,9,Fand walking. There have been a number
OL,10,Fof plans put forward to improve that,
OL,11,Fwhich we haven't seen.
OL,13,F"The coroner made the point that as
OL,14,Fthe number of people cycling increases
OL,15,Fwe don't have an extensive safe
OL,16,Fnetwork to accompany that."
OL,18,FA vigil was held shortly after his
OL,19,Fdeath by friends and the cycling
OL,20,Fcommunity.
