OL,7,FA permanent memorial to Gary McMahon
OL,8,Fnow sits at the junction where he
OL,9,Fdied. A white bike which its creator
OL,10,FJohn Wright says stands as a permanent
OL,11,Freminder of the dangers of the road.
OL,13,F"It could have been me, I cycle every
OL,14,Fday, come rain or shine and I've been
OL,15,Fknocked off and the driver has said he
OL,16,Fdidn't see me. It is normal and my
OL,17,Fnext bike ride could be my last," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
